title: "String interpolation produces a debug description for an optional value; did you mean to make this explicit?"
content:
![Screen Shot 2020-07-08 at 23 06 18](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/31644638/86928574-ae6b0000-c16f-11ea-8549-c1da09e4f48f.png)

```diff
default:
-   fatalError("Unexpected Segue identifier; \(segue.identifier)")
+   fatalError("Unexpected Segue identifier; \(String(describing: segue.identifier))")
```
